f.v: The Global Legal Entity Identifier Foundation (GLEIF) was established by the Financial Stability Board (FSB) in June 2014 as a not-for-profit organization to support the implementation and use of the Legal Entity Identifier (LEI). GLEIF enables smarter, less costly and more reliable decisions about who to do business with by supporting the implementation of the LEI and the availability of the Global LEI Index. GLEIF is headquartered in Basel, Switzerland.
